    "\n",
    "### Producción\n",
    "```python\n",
    "# FastAPI wrapper\n",
    "from fastapi import FastAPI\n",
    "app = FastAPI()\n",
    "_d = PhishingDetector()\n",
    "\n",
    "@app.get('/check')\n",
    "def check(url: str): return _d.explain(url)\n",
    "```\n"
